result.name: Shamrock Hotel

reviews.text: It's a well cleaned and nice hotel. But the rooms might be a bit small. Looks old on the outside but new on the inside. Also very convenient just beside exit C1 of Jordan station. 🙂

Great service, great location and polite staff, always smile and very helpful. The hotel also give us a bottle of wine regarding our weeding anniversary! We very appreciate the kind gesture. Overall we are very satisfied and appreciate the service! 😁😄😍😀
Lovely clean and modern hotel. Would recommend going to shamrock hotel to freind and family.  Up to date to technology with easy controls for AC and lighting.

Very pleasant accommodation.Very friendy staff. Quiet and clean rooms and tasty buffet breakfast. Great location, short walk distance temple street night market area and about 15-20 minute walk to waterfront. MTR Jordan exit C1 just behind the corner.

A relatively small hotel at Nathan road with quite spacy rooms (for HK standard) and a big service. The staffs are nice, the food quality is great, the location is superb, just few meters from Jordan MTR C1 exit. Definitely will consider Shamrock for the next family trip.

result.adr_address: Hong Kong, 佐敦彌敦道223號新樂酒店閣樓
result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, 佐敦彌敦道223號新樂酒店閣樓
result.name: Shamrock Cafe

reviews.text: The Shamrock Cafe is a buffet restaurant that serves Western cuisine. We came on a weekday evening and we were able to get a table. Service was fast, and we were served our meals quickly. The menu rotates frequently, and the dishes change every so often. I had the prime rib, cooked medium, and it came out medium rare, so I had to get out reheated. Not a huge deal since it was quickly fixed. The buffet selection was pretty good; there were breads, salads, hot drinks, and desserts. Overall the Shamrock Cafe was decent and I world return again.
We used the Shamrock Cafe for our accomodation included breakfast. The breakfast is well prepared, with a good combination of Asian and Western style of food.
Semi-buffet dinner with soup & salad bar👍20% discount on menu, food quality ok & good value for money… location is good, just at Jordan station.
Very nice place & location to stay.very near at MTR (train stn) & the breakfast buffet is awesome.😊👍👍 Highly Recommended.👍👍
Breakfast buffet price is very seasonable, only $126 (included 20%off ). Foods are fresh and tasty. Western style, Indian style and Chinese style all you can eat.

雖然沙律吧 & 甜品選擇不多，但菜很新鮮。
特別推介 - 格仔餅，很脆，比很多街外賣的好吃多； 懷舊涼粉 - 小時候的口感。  
主菜十分不錯，尤其是牛扒及羊扒，真的可以做到要求的生熟度。  
座位不太擠，服務特別殷勤，比5星級酒店還要好，高CP值👍

result.adr_address: 香港佐敦彌敦道223號
result.name: 新樂酒店

reviews.text: スタッフの対応は丁寧。部屋も適度に広くて、湯船も綺麗。値段も良い。エントランスも適度な広さ。周辺には色んな施設があり、街の雰囲気が楽しめる。
地鐵佐敦站C1 位於隔壁1分鐘，服務人員都非常親切，熱心，房間乾淨，12:00提早CHECk in ,也都通融，甚至無償升等，下次必定回住。要找到熱誠的香港服務 人員，只有在這裡。
C1出口上がってすぐなので大変便利。但し階段しかないので重い荷物があるときは、遠回りになるが、道路向かい側の出口から回って来るのがよい。清潔でサービス精神のあるよいホテル。
服務人員都非常親切、熱情，因為我自己的問題所以入住手續有出錯，但是所有人員都非常耐心、和善的處理，將問題迅速解決，能感受到都是用真心去對待每一位客人，感受非常好，再加上交通位置實在是太方便了，所以大大推薦，下次再到香港仍會列為第一優先考量的住宿！
It's a well cleaned and nice hotel. But the rooms might be a bit small. Looks old on the outside but new on the inside. Also very convenient just beside exit C1 of Jordan station. 🙂
